page.title: 19CONTINUED
page.content:
At 5.00 p.m., he leaves the office for home, arriving home at 5.25 p.m. evening meal is ready at 6.00 p.m. After the meal, he did some gardening and made a poultry run. At 8.00 p.m., he denailed 2 x 2 spars ( for working next weekend.) After that, he saw the children to bed at 8.30 p.m. at 8.45 p.m., he drinks some coffee and watches television. At 11.00 p.m., Mr. Seddon goes to bed.
SUNDAY 16/6/85. MRS. WILSON - HOUSEWIFE.
8.40 a.m. - Got up. Set breakfast table for four. Put dishwasher on. 9.00 a.m. - Prepared breakfast. Grapefruit, bolied eggs and toast. 9.30 a.m. - Wash and dress.
